    "title": "关于新增《京东开放平台旗舰店商家考核规范》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1373913914467663872",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<div style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: #262626; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>您好，为适应业务发展需求，将新增《京东开放平台旗舰店商家考核规范》。现进行规则公示，<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">公示期：2026年5月21日- </span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">2026年5月27日，<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">规则预计于2026年5月28日生效，</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"> </span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: #262626; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\">核心内容：<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit;\">旗舰店的详细考核规则及影响<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"> </span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; color: #262626; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: inherit; padding: inherit;\">具体规则如下：</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台旗舰店商家考核规范</span></strong></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第一章 概述</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">目的及依据</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">为保障平台（域名为jd.com）健康发展，促进平台与商家共同成长，持续为消费者提供优质的商品、品牌和服务，根据国家法律法规规范，以及&ldquo;京东 JD.COM&rdquo;开放平台服务协议、《京东开放平台规则总则》等相关协议和规则，特制定《京东开放平台旗舰店商家考核规范》。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">适用范围</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">适用于平台内所有的旗舰店商家（包含大药房旗舰店），以及因考核不达标被从旗舰店降级的商家。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第二章 实施细则</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核对象</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台内所有的旗舰店、大药房旗舰店商家均需参加，且需符合对应考核标准，如未达标，将会被从旗舰店降级为专卖店，大药房旗舰店降级为专营店（被降级的商家将无法自行申请店铺类型升级）。新入驻的旗舰店商家享有开店90天内免考期，开店90天后自动进入正式考核范围。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">因考核不达标被从旗舰店降级的商家可继续参加考核，下一考核周期考核达标后，平台会恢复该店铺的旗舰店身份（无需商家自行申请升级）。如未达标，将继续维持现有店铺类型。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核规则</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核周期：自然月内每双周为一个考核周期</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核指标：双周内平均店铺星级</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">店铺星级口径：剔除<strong>默认赋星商家和无星级商家</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.3 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核结果</span></strong></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">若店铺达标，则维持旗舰店资格。</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">若店铺不达标（店铺星级&le;4星），则直接执行降级处理。</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">已降级店铺仍继续考核，若在后续的考核中，双周内店铺星级持续&ge;4.2星，平台会恢复该店铺的旗舰店身份（无需商家自行申请升级）。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.3 </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核影响</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家店铺类型因旗舰店考核发生变更（包含考核不达标从旗舰店降级和降级商家考核达标的升级两种情形）后，存在以下相关影响：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">店铺命名规范需要符合对应店铺类型的命名规范要求。详情可参考</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=2598\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">京东开放平台店铺命名及信息规范</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">。</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">从旗舰店降级的商家，在店铺类型降级期间，不可发布仅允许旗舰店类型发布的类目/品牌商品。有旗舰店经营要求的类目/品牌，具体可见</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=826299126802157568\"><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">京东开放平台商品类目管理规范</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">。</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述相关影响外，店铺由旗舰店降级后，平台将依据与降级后店铺类型有关的规则对店铺进行管理。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">另外，若商家存在违反法律法规要求、或违反平台规则可能或已经造成平台风险或消费者权益受损的，平台有权对店铺类型做降级处理，包含但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0px;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家收到涉及侵权、售假、虚构或夸大产品功效、所售商品抽检不合格等违反法律法规的处罚，及涉及监管处罚、产生重大负面舆情等；</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家发布容易造成消费者产生混淆的商品和信息的行为，造成一定负向影响的；</span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家服务能力、经营状态持续不佳，包括但不限于店铺星级较低、经营指标达不到旗舰店相关要求等。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第三章 附则</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.2 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东可根据运营情况随时调整本规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有约定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无约定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议；若商家服务协议约定的违约金金额高于规则约定的，京东有权适用协议约定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.4 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本规则于2026年5月21日新增，于2026年5月28日生效。</span></p>\n</div>",
